*                NOTE: Depth > 1000mm AA = Depth(mm)/100
*          b  =  Web Thickness. a=4mm,b=5mm,c=6mm,d=8mm,e=10mm,f=12mm,g=16mm,h=20mm
*         CC  =  Flange Width(mm)/10
*         DD  =  Flange Thickness (mm)
